{"tid":236802,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[千古迷題] 究竟關公隻赤兔馬死果時係幾多歲？","createTime":"2017-05-10T03:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T13:17:56.000Z","uid":44160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2d07ee122835c4ea3ab17ee1ba2a015c54dec0","tid":236802,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"我細細個睇三國就已經成日諗，赤兔馬細個果陣就跟董卓，後生就跟呂布，中年就跟關公，關公仲要騎住廿幾三十年，到關公死左之後，隻馬都仲要過多一排，唔肯食野自殺先死。呢隻馬至少都應該有40歲，以馬黎講都幾痴線，應該可以叫馬的yoda大師。係到我想問全知的連登仔，有冇人知呢隻傳奇赤兔馬究竟死時幾多歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2675360b1d9825137f655cb25839c68e3bb7d702","tid":236802,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"48歲(赤瘁)，oK?滿意未?三國虛構假嫁D奶"},{"pid":"871a69fb2dd537b009ae1bc059fc4d4986115303","tid":236802,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:58:26.000Z","msg":"真心咩？"},{"pid":"5cac0e695b7a5664a1bb07258ce99152172da6c7","tid":236802,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45447a73295ae25998685b960ffdebb893aec7cf","tid":236802,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"樓豬假膠"},{"pid":"f9add9e0ce825a4c96309945ad54e2d58f909d38","tid":236802,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解d馬名可以咁型<br />\n絕影的盧爪黃飛電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四大神馬<br />\n絕影仲永遠立於不倒之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307759fdcc4554596ec27129de5f232fed3c669d","tid":236802,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:10:42.000Z","msg":"講真乜古時d馬長命d架咩？而家馬會d馬隻隻都係得十幾歲命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im